      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior retains a strong shine, though you may find a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car is sound; it starts reliably, shifts smoothly, and has a complete service history. It is a dependable, high-quality vehicle that offers a great balance of performance and value for its next owner.",
