    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved over the years\u2014it runs like a dream and is totally ready for its next adventure! If you\u2019re looking for a dependable, comfortable car that\u2019s been treated right, you\u2019ve found it. I'd love for it to go to a great new home, so feel free to reach out if you want to come see it!",
      "price": 33500.0,
