      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound A80 Supra Turbo featuring the legendary 2JZ-GTE power plant. This unit maintains its factory sequential twin-turbo configuration, delivering linear power through the robust Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis remains rigid, benefiting from a Torsen limited-slip differential that ensures optimal torque distribution under load. Recent service includes a comprehensive timing belt replacement and a full fluid flush, ensuring the high-pressure fuel system and cooling loops are operating within factory specifications. While exhibiting minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain integrity and compression across all six cylinders remain exceptional for the discerning driver.",
